We believe that every detail matters when it comes to creating a truly unforgettable experience.

The retreat will be for your exclusive use, we will never ask you to share your space. The main house, which is a minimum stay requirement, accommodates up to 16 people. For larger groups there is the option to add on additional rooms. If the upper level rooms or the Annexe are not required they will simply be locked.

Prices are based on a 7 night stay and include cleaning and linen. During September through to May we can be flexible and offer a minimum of a 2 night stay. Cleaning charges apply for stays of less than 4 nights.

Early Bird Booking (12 months in advance of stay) 5% discount available!

MAIN HOUSE

The main house is arranged over two levels accommodating 16 people in bedrooms 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 (Bedroom 6 does not have a bathroom).

  • 2 Night Stay £3600
  • 3 Night Stay £4000
  • 4 Night Stay £4400
  • 5 Night Stay £4800
  • 6 Night Stay £5200
  • 7 Night Stay £5800

For stays of less than 4 nights, cleaning charges apply £550.

LEVEL 3 ROOMS

Bedrooms 7, 8, 9 can be added for larger groups exceeding 16. Level 3 rooms are optional and will be locked if not required.

  • 2 Night Stay £130 per room
  • 3 Night Stay £390 per room
  • 4 Night Stay £260 per room
  • 5 Night Stay £325 per room
  • 6 Night Stay £390 per room
  • 7 Night Stay £455 per room

For stays of less than 4 nights, cleaning charges apply £55 per room.

ANNEXE

The perfect add on for larger groups. Bedroom 10 has an ensuite bathroom and lounge area. This room has with 2 double beds or 4 single beds.

  • 2 Night Stay £270
  • 3 Night Stay £405
  • 4 Night Stay £540
  • 5 Night Stay £675
  • 6 Night Stay £810
  • 7 Night Stay £945

For stays of less than 4 nights, cleaning charges apply £105 per room.

If you are a retreat facilitator hosting your own retreat, please contact us for special packages.

REQUEST TO BOOK
DEPOSIT

To secure your booking 25% deposit is required, with the remaining balance to be paid 8 weeks prior to arrival.
Damage security deposit £1000 per group/£100 per person for same sex groups and groups of 25 years and under.
To be returned no later than 7 working days after departure.

NB: If you choose not to use the upper level rooms and the annexe they will simply be locked.

OPTIONAL EXTRAS

During the winter season pool heating is available, priced at £50 per day (minimum 5 days).
Maid service is available £140 (up to 6 hours) booking in advance is essential.

EXTRAS INCLUDED

If you’re traveling with infants we offer a bed guard, four travel cots and 2 guest beds that
can be positioned in any bedroom. We also include a selection of infant equipment including,
high chairs, baby monitors, baby bath, changing mat, steriliser, playpen, baby walker, linen and towels.

Beach towels and all sports equipment is also provided.
